# TypeScript Rules

Prefer strict types. When editing modules see [[coding-standards]] for the
shared style guide.

Reuse the logger from @src/utils/logger.ts instead of console.log, and follow
the template in @src/templates/service-template.ts.

Do not reach into @engram/memory-interchange internals — import from its public
barrel only. Never decorate DTOs with @Deprecated in this codebase.
